sentences: James Lee Baker (born May 19, 1996), better known as BlocBoy JB, is an American rapper.
He is best known for his song "Look Alive" (featuring Drake), which peaked at number 5 on the Billboard Hot 100 chart in 2018.
James Baker was born on May 19, 1996, in Memphis, Tennessee.

sentences: His name comes from his father, who is currently serving a 25-year prison sentence for rape.
